How to Install.

1. Copy to ~/.config

$ cp -r mpvfb ~/.config/


2. Launch mpv with this custom command.

$ mpv --config-dir=$HOME/.config/mpvfb --player-operation-mode=pseudo-gui --script=/$HOME/.config/mpvfb/scripts/user-input.lua 


3. Press Ctrl+o to show directory (default to $HOME).


4. Navigate with arrow keys.


5. Enter your desired location by press Alt+o.
